rks<a class=3D"headerlink" href=3D"https://benavlabs.github.io/crudadmin/us=
age/common-patterns/#why-this-e-commerce-pattern-works" title=3D"Permanent =
link">=C2=B6</a></h4>
<ol>
<li><strong>Business logic validation</strong>: Price/cost validation in sc=
hemas</li>
<li><strong>Enum handling</strong>: Order status as proper enums</li>
<li><strong>Decimal precision</strong>: Proper handling of money values</li=
>
<li><strong>Scalable session backend</strong>: Redis for high traffic</li>
<li><strong>Larger page sizes</strong>: Better for inventory management</li=
>
</ol>
